  - m_Id: 2416123601219584
    m_Localized: Max units +10
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686376591360
    m_Localized: Welcome to Galaxy Scavengers.\nClickon the screen.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534400
    m_Localized: Use <color=#FFC107>WASD keys</color> to move the main unit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534401
    m_Localized: Great!\nUse the <color=#FFC107>mouse wheel</color> to zoom in and
      out.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534402
    m_Localized: Press the <color=#FFC107>Space key</color> or <color=#FFC107>click
      the icon</color> to pause time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534403
    m_Localized: Move the main unit near a resource block, then <color=#FFC107>click
      a resource block</color> to start mining.\nTry mining 10 units of gray <color=#DBD1C7>Ferrite</color>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534404
    m_Localized: Resource blocks are scattered across the map - keep exploring so
      you never run short of materials to mine.\n<color=#DBD1C7>(Click the screen
      to continue)</color>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534405
    m_Localized: <color=#FFC107>Click the screen</color> to fire an energy shot.\nHold
      the button to fire continuously.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534406
    m_Localized: Good.\nNow click the <color=#FFC107>Seed Core</color> at the center
      and produce one <color=#FFC107>Miner Unit</color>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534407
    m_Localized: A <color=#FFC107>Miner Unit</color> automatically mines the nearest
      resource and hauls it to the closest storage.\n<color=#DBD1C7>(Click the screen
      to continue)</color>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534408
    m_Localized: Click the Seed Core again and produce 2 <color=#FFC107>Construct
      Units</color>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534409
    m_Localized: Great.\nClick the <color=#FFC107>Basic Buildings button</color>,
      select a <color=#FFC107>Storage</color>, and place it near the base.\nOnce
      placed, <color=#FFC107>Construct Units</color> will automatically haul resources
      and begin building.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534410
    m_Localized: <color=#FFC107>Right-clicking</color> the screen deselects the current
      building or UI, and <color=#FF7043>right-click-dragging</color> removes any
      buildings or units within the area.\n<color=#DBD1C7>(Click the screen to continue)</color>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534411
    m_Localized: Now let's process the resources you've mined into higher-tier materials.\nProcessing
      requires power.\nSelect a <color=#FFC107>Generator</color> and place it so
      that a Storage or the Seed Core falls within its light-blue range.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534412
    m_Localized: Next, select a <color=#FFC107>Smelter</color> and place it within
      the Generator's range.\nA Generator supplies power to all buildings inside
      its range.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534413
    m_Localized: Finally, click the Seed Core and produce 1 <color=#FFC107>Process
      Unit</color>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534414
    m_Localized: Production buildings like the <color=#FFC107>Smelter</color> require
      an assigned <color=#FFC107>Process Unit</color> before they can process resources.\nProcess
      Units are automatically assigned to empty production buildings.\n<color=#DBD1C7>(Click
      the screen to continue)</color>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534415
    m_Localized: Process Units will fetch resources from a nearby storage and begin
      processing.\nClick the <color=#FFC107>Smelter</color> you just built and queue
      <color=#DBD1C7>5 Alloy Plates</color>.\nCtrl-click to adjust in increments
      of 10, Shift-click for 100.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2421686418534416
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've mastered the basics of Galaxy Scavengers.\nAll
      that's left is to place Extractors on the cyan tiles, extract as much data
      as possible, and escape the planet.\nGood luck.\n<color=#DBD1C7>(Click the
      screen to close)</color>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
